{"tid":1967510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去沙嶺公墓的交通/懶人包","createTime":"2020-04-11T03:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T04:58:38.000Z","uid":344775,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf91e601d2774922d0de3a45f60dff5d1ea926b","tid":1967510,"uid":344775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"近日去了沙嶺公墓，搵路搵左好耐，於是整左個懶人包比有心的同路人。<br />\n<br />\n物資準備：<br />\n<br />\n買花買香的可以去上水站附近個街市（a出口），係2樓，lift口一出就見到d鋪頭。<br />\n<br />\n係羅湖道站出的話沿路入沙嶺公墓也有花買（行到死，千萬唔好）<br />\n<br />\n交通：<br />\n上水巴士站坐 73k 巴士係沙嶺站落車。<br />\n你只要係沙嶺站落車，你成功左90%！！！ <br />\n<br />\n唔建議坐小巴，1等候時間好長，2有當地市民坐部車回家，唔好阻到市民。<br />\n<br />\n沙嶺站落車，不用過馬路，附近沿建築地行盤行，轉右就可以了，約10分鐘內。見附圖。<br />\n<br />\n落車向建築地盤行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9ATfVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9ATfVz.jpg&h=3d9ea169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7nRM2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7nRM2c.jpg&h=118df405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcHVufw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcHVufw.jpg&h=ab8f139d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGRZVVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGRZVVv.jpg&h=0812d5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oLTfZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oLTfZf.jpg&h=07e4bd33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0S2TK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0S2TK5.jpg&h=6c459816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，如果真係有手足係羅湖站出想買花同元寶，落車就有一檔，請一路沿路直行，見到公墓立石，向右行，佢會提示有2012年的公墓同 巴士站73k方向，直行行到出大路的時候，望向你左方，應該有公墓綠色banner提示，向果條小路一直行，你會找到手足的。需時，我諗有20分鐘以上。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾小畫家技巧請勿bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，不捉鬼不分化，不是看到希望才堅持，堅持才能看到希望。 <br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"3fefcef668fc6d7e5dcfed295ed9d08920dfe15b","tid":1967510,"uid":322135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n有用資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4f86ccd284a5d73e30038db7240ccda9293c4c","tid":1967510,"uid":344775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fefcef668fc6d7e5dcfed295ed9d08920dfe15b","tid":1967510,"uid":322135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n有用資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T05:48:41.000Z","msg":"謝，昨天去都見好多中年手足去<br />\n有個要用手仗都去，有心"},{"pid":"ee066abff241146c94a3b9e4a91d73b006775a2f","tid":1967510,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"ac02f3354d4a62d2fe43f678d2a3251c2817948e","tid":1967510,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打"},{"pid":"7168d20567b47651e9742f192ccaba7dcddd7e98","tid":1967510,"uid":50873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"啱啱去完<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"2570cd6d4cfb2ab62278864313b4370339ee87ef","tid":1967510,"uid":267953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:37:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ed7e39491eb814b587a46765fef93268161e5a1","tid":1967510,"uid":291579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:41:13.000Z","msg":"推唔到都推"},{"pid":"7fc41233913faff3103072426af91ce9533c55b8","tid":1967510,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46b5c8048d3bb067bcfeccc1ccccbe0ec70251e","tid":1967510,